Package: parthian
Type: Package
Title: Landscape connectivity using energy costs of travel
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2024-03-27
Author: Emilio Berti <emilio.berti@idiv.de>
Maintainer: Emilio Berti <emilio.berti@idiv.de>
Description: Calculate cost of travel (kcal) in a landscape for an animal, use 
  this to find the least-cost paths between locations, e.g. protected areas, 
  and evaluate the spatial network of such areas. Finally, it ranks areas
  according the several network centrality measures.
